"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-05-france-set-olympic-mens-football-final-spain\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LYON, France (AFP) - Jean-Philippe Mateta scored twice as hosts France came from behind to beat Egypt 3-1 after extra time on Monday and set up an Olympic men's football final showdown with Spain, who edged Morocco 2-1.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32045441389176e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thierry Henry's France looked to be heading for defeat in their semi-final in Lyon after Mahmoud Saber put Egypt ahead against the run of play just after the hour mark.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.53887292285669e-15, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.929165778798523e-12, \"text\": \"Saber\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\"}, {\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Crystal Palace striker Mateta levelled late on to force extra time, in which he headed France in front after Egypt's Omar Fayed was sent off.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 512, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"score\": 0.9999090202825526, \"rank\": 9.097822614096783e-05, \"text\": \"Omar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Olise then sealed the win on 108 minutes and France, looking for their second Olympic men's football gold medal and first since 1984, will now face Spain at the Parc des Princes in Paris on Friday.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Olise\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32045441389176e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.61711808259565e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you see France picking up medals all over the place, you say to yourself it is up to us now to not let everyone down,\\\" said France coach Henry.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not want to be the team who do not win a medal so at least that is done.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now we will see what colour we get, but honestly I am living a dream here and I do not want to wake up.\\\"\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France hit the woodwork through Loic Bade late in the first half and were caught out by a sucker punch when Saber fired Egypt ahead against the run of play on 62 minutes.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"score\": 0.9602388887650241, \"rank\": 0.04140726902715154, \"text\": \"Bade\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.929165778798523e-12, \"text\": \"Saber\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabre\"}, {\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts then pushed frantically for an equaliser and struck the woodwork twice in a matter of seconds, captain Alexandre Lacazette heading off a post and Bade nodding the follow-up against the bar.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexandre Lacazette\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\"}, {\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"score\": 0.9602388887650241, \"rank\": 0.04140726902715154, \"text\": \"Bade\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The leveller arrived in the 83rd minute, with new Bayern Munich signing Olise the creator as he cut through the middle on a driving run before playing in Mateta to finish.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France hoped to find a winner before extra time, but a penalty appeal after Fayed blocked a Bade header with his hand was dismissed after a long VAR review.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"score\": 0.9602388887650241, \"rank\": 0.04140726902715154, \"text\": \"Bade\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.850460126684335e-44, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Egypt were quickly reduced to 10 men in extra time when Fayed - already booked for arguing against the penalty call - saw yellow again for chopping down Desire Doue.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1787, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2573433239152392e-17, \"text\": \"Desire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\"}, {\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doue,_Seine-et-Marne\", \"score\": 0.858682698055531, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Doue\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doue,_Seine-et-Marne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doue,_Seine-et-Marne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France went ahead in the 99th minute when Kiliann Sildillia headed Olise's delivery back across goal for Mateta to head in his fourth goal of the tournament.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.514180522330679e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Egypt and Morocco to fight for bronze -The excellent Olise fired in the third at the start of the second half of extra time after a clearance struck Doue and fell into his path and France celebrated wildly at full-time.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2840437309240044e-21, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0397461581812396e-18,