ource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0397461581812396e-18, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.84549122261346e-19, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco had led through a Soufiane Rahimi penalty towards the end of the first half, a sixth goal at the Olympics for the tournament's top scorer, and his fourth to come from the spot.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0397461581812396e-18, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That sent the large Moroccan support at the Stade Velodrome wild, but Spain kept their cool to equalise through their own star man in the 66th minute.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2683, \"end\": 2691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2055036690564475e-17, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2733, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32045441389176e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fermin Lopez, a member of Spain's triumphant Euro 2024 squad, who scored twice in the Olympic quarter-final against Japan, pounced in the 66th minute when the ball broke loose in the box and fired low into the net to make it 1-1.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2815, \"end\": 2821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.523656374897788e-13, \"text\": \"Fermin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\"}, {\"begin\": 2822, \"end\": 2827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.752169517005788, \"rank\": 0.3292654049202037, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}, {\"begin\": 2841, \"end\": 2846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32045441389176e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9992557690468441, \"rank\": 0.000744785245490609, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the prospect of extra time looming, Spain won it in the 85th minute as Lopez found Sanchez bounding into the area, and he sent a shot low into the far corner.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3087, \"end\": 3092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32045441389176e-15, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.752169517005788, \"rank\": 0.3292654049202037, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco now go to Nantes for the bronze medal match on Thursday against their North African rivals Egypt.\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0397461581812396e-18, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3229, \"end\": 3235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2115981837735677e-15, \"text\": \"Nantes\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\"}, {\"begin\": 3310, \"end\": 3315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_na